page.title: 09MY TUESDAY
page.content: First I wake up at{07:30}I have a lie in for about 10 minutes then I get up, get dressed and have my breakfast. I get a lift to school with my dad he is a self employed builder.We get into class at{09:00}.Normally we do Maths or English in the morning,we have playtime at{10:40}.Then after play we carry on with our work , after dinner play we have singing , then the boys have health studies while the girls have netball.After play we have football and the girls go for their singing .We go straight home after football. When I get home I don't do much I just watch T.V. and eat.I normally have tea at around{18:00}, then I go to bed at about{21:00}or a little later.
